verbose_text: To further determine the role of Tfam in Treg mediated tumor immunity, we co-transferred CD25 depleted total splenic cells (from CD45.1/CD45.1 C57BL/6 mice) with control or Tfam deficient Tregs (CD45.2/CD45.2) to Rag1 -/- recipient mice that were injected with B16-OVA tumor cells (XREF_FIG).
evidence: CD25-depleted total splenic cells (from CD45.1/CD45.1 C57BL/6 mice) with control or Tfam
